<function>

access:   protected

name: _save

param: string, $class

param: string, $event

param: string, $descr

return: mixed

</function>

Support method to save (write) an event and message to the log.

* Parameters:

 * string //$class//: The class name reporting the event.

 * string //$event//: The event type (e.g. 'info' or 'debug').

 * string //$descr//: A description of the event.

* Returns mixed: Boolean false if the event was not saved (usually because it was not recognized), or a non-empty value if it was saved.

Appends to the file, and uses an exclusive lock (LOCK_EX).